prompts.frontCover: A charming, flat 2D watercolor painting of a very round, fluffy, cartoon-style hamster struggling to climb a small, wobbly stack of brightly colored macarons. The hamster, painted with soft brown and white flowing colors, has a determined but slightly exasperated expression. A single macaron has fallen to the side. The scene is set against a clean, white background with subtle paper texture and organic paint bleeds. In the center, written in a beautiful, readable, dark teal handwritten cursive script, is the text "happy birthday". The overall style is lighthearted and humorous, with artistic brush strokes and soft, cheerful colors.
